# HAMSA Dashboard Access

- The actual HAMSA app iframe must never be embedded in the FREE Dashboard, including localhost.
- Localhost must mirror production access behavior.
- The FREE Dashboard HAMSA route must show the preview/locked marketing page only.
- Only REGEN/AMRITA dashboard users may load the actual HAMSA app iframe.
- Do not use `admin` role as a bypass for HAMSA app access. Admin tooling access is separate from HAMSA entitlement.
- Admin Dashboard may expose the actual HAMSA app only through a dedicated admin testing route, never by bypassing the FREE/member dashboard HAMSA gate.
- Do not change REGEN/free trial gating or entitlement behavior when working on HAMSA layout, iframe, mobile/desktop switching, or fullscreen behavior.
